          strong Work-in-Progress
        p Success Academy is a network of world-class charter schools serving New York City. After working as the front-end developer of the successacademies.org site, I was asked to do strategy, UX, and design of the Success Academies Careers site. In the requirements for the new site, we outlined four major goals: 
        ul
          li Motivate potential candidates to apply
          li Set candidates up for success during the hiring process
          li Inspire candidates so they are primed to accept an offer
          li Establish relevance to a millennial audience
       

