            .wolf-item-inner
                p.figcaption In the first section of the research, I presented an analysis of how other companies are accomplishing the goals we outlined. In the second section, I researched special considerations the client requested we look into, and finally, I looked at their current sites analytics.
                a(href='' target='_blank')
          .wolf-item.is-caption.is-caption--right(data-speed="-1")
            .wolf-item-inner
